data.description: Welcome to Empire Estates! This lovely townhome has a thoughtful layout, offering 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, an open concept living, kitchen, and dining area, as well as a large patio in the fenced yard. This home also features underground sprinklers, washer and dryer, and 2 hot water heaters for those who love taking long showers! The quiet neighborhood also offers a walking path, community playground and park. This home is conveniently located in the highly desirable Peterson School District and is close to many shopping and grocery stores. Come take a look! For more information or to schedule a showing, please contact Janna Pummill at 406-546-3144 or your real estate professional.
